# how to run the darn thing

- u gotta start frontend and backend
- cd to frontend, then game, and then run `npm install` (only have to install once)
- after that's done, to start front end use `npm start`
- open another terminal
- (only done once) set up ur venv if on windows unless you're robbie and don't care (`python -m venv venv`)
- if windows run Set-ExecuionPolicy unrestricted 
- start your venv with `venv\Scripts\activate` if you're on windows and use virtual environments
- run `pip install flask`, `pip install flask_cors`, `pip install socketio`, and anything else u need to (only do this once)
- cd to backend
- run `python main.py` to start backend server